    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><ex>H</ex><abbr>umani</abbr><ex>ssimo</ex></expan> potentissi<lb break="no" n="2"/>mo adque <note>sic</note> piissimo <lb n="3"/>vere victoriumque <lb n="4"/>clementissimo <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>omino</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>n</abbr><ex>ostro</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>G</abbr><ex>aio</ex></expan> Valerio <lb n="6"/>Maximiano <expan><abbr>P</abbr><ex>io</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>F</abbr><ex>elici</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usto</ex></expan> <lb n="7"/><expan><abbr>Fl</abbr><ex>avius</ex></expan> Severianus <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>ir</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>erfectissimus</ex></expan> <lb n="8"/><expan><abbr>praes</abbr><ex>es</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Is</abbr><ex>auriae</ex></expan> numini eius <lb n="9"/>semper dedicatus </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <supplied reason="lost">ἡ β</supplied>ουλὴ καὶ ὁ δῆμο<supplied reason="lost">ς ἐτείμη</supplied><lb break="no" n="2"/><supplied reason="lost">σαν</supplied> Πό(πλιον) Αἴλιον Ἡιόδωρον παρ<supplied reason="lost">ά</supplied><lb break="no" n="3"/><supplied reason="lost">δο</supplied>ξον πανκρατιαστήν ξυστάρχ<supplied reason="lost">ην</supplied> <lb n="4"/><supplied reason="lost">τῶ</supplied>ν ἐν Λακεδαίμονι ἀγώνων <lb n="5"/><supplied reason="lost">νι</supplied>κήσαντα Ὀλύμπεια τὰ ἐν Ἀ<lb break="no" n="6"/><supplied reason="lost">θή</supplied>ναις Ἀντιόχειαν τὸν Εὐκρατια<lb break="no" n="7"/><supplied reason="lost">νὸ</supplied>ν βʹ Ἀλεξάνδρειαν Σμύρναν <lb n="8"/>Ἁλία τὰ ἐν Ῥόδῳ ἀνδρῶν πανκράτιν <lb n="9"/>Πέργαμον Ἔφεσον Βαρβίλλεια <lb n="10"/>Ἐφέσεια τὰ μεγάλα Νέαν Πόλιν <lb n="11"/>Ποτιόλους Εὐσέβεια δίς τὴν ἐν Ἄργε<supplied reason="lost">ι</supplied> <lb n="12"/>ἀσπίδα Καισάρεια ἐν δίς Λακε<lb break="no" n="13"/>δαίμονα πάλην πανκράτην Θήβας πά<lb break="no" n="14"/>λην πανκράτην Τράλλεις πάλην πα<supplied reason="lost">ν</supplied><lb break="no" n="15"/>κράτην Ἴσθμια καὶ Νεμία ἱερὰν <lb n="16"/>ἀνδρῶν πανκράτην καὶ ἄλλους <lb n="17"/>ἀγῶνας ταλαντιαίους λϛʹ <lb n="18"/>Ταρσὸν γʹ
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Eine griechische Inschrift befindet sich auf der Vorderseite, die lateinische auf der Rückseite der Basis. Datierung der griechischen Ehreninschrift: 130-170. Z. 3: auch victori (omni)umque denkbar.</p>
            </div>
